        {"key": "tutorial.step1", "value": "You just arrived in the city with $500 and a dream.\nMegaCorp controls everything. Every shop, every customer.\nBut you have something they don't \u2014 a deck of cards\nthat will build your empire.\n\nYOUR GOAL: Control 6 out of 10 market territories.\nLet's begin."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step2", "value": "This is your battlefield \u2014 the market table.\nAt the top: 10 TERRITORY blocks. Control 6 to WIN.\nBlue = yours. Red = MegaCorp's. Gray = up for grabs."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step3", "value": "These are your cards \u2014 your weapons.\nEach turn you draw 5 cards. You can play 3 of them."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step4", "value": "BLUE cards are Businesses \u2014 they make money.\nGREEN cards are Employees \u2014 they boost businesses.\nRED cards are Actions \u2014 instant powerful effects.\nPURPLE cards are Upgrades \u2014 permanent improvements."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step5", "value": "See that blue DINER card? Drag it to one of the\nempty business slots on the table.\nGO ON \u2014 grab it and place it!"},
        {"key": "tutorial.step6", "value": "NICE! Your Diner is open for business!\nIt earns $50 every turn and attracts 3 customers.\nCustomers = market share = territories = WINNING."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step7", "value": "You used 1 action. See the green dots?\nYou have 2 actions left this turn.\nPlay more cards or..."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step8", "value": "...press END TURN to let the market do its thing.\nYour businesses will earn money, pay employees,\nand fight MegaCorp for customers."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step9", "value": "Watch the magic happen:\n1. Your businesses produce income\n2. Customers flow to whoever has more to offer\n3. Territories shift based on customer count\n4. MegaCorp makes their move"},
        {"key": "tutorial.step10", "value": "See that? Your money changed!\n$50 income from Diner\n-$15 salary for your Intern\n-$5 tax (15% of income)\n= $30 profit this turn!"},
        {"key": "tutorial.step11", "value": "Now MegaCorp plays. They're building too.\nWatch what they do \u2014 knowing your enemy is key."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step12", "value": "Need better cards? Press SHOP to buy new ones.\nStronger cards = better combos = more profit.\nBut don't go broke \u2014 save money for emergencies!"},
        {"key": "tutorial.step13", "value": "Tips to dominate:\n\n\u2022 Place Barista in Coffee Shop = LATTE ART combo (+$40!)\n\u2022 Accountant cuts your tax in half\n\u2022 Watch out \u2014 Hacker earns big but FBI might raid you\n\u2022 6 territories = YOU WIN. Go get 'em!"},
        {"key": "tutorial.step14", "value": "The market is yours for the taking.\nBuild. Hire. Combo. Dominate.\n\nGood luck, entrepreneur!"},
